'''Kurgoth Hellspawn''' was a [[half-fiend]] [[fire giant]] who led the assault upon the [[drow]] city of [[Maerimydra]] and with the aid of [[Duneth Wharreil]] managed to sack the entire city. Although the drow of Maerimydra suffered from [[Silence of Lolth|Lolth's Silence]], leading his army of [[ogre]]s, fire giants and [[demon]]s to victory is an impressive feat nonetheless.
